.TH "vidioc_querycap" 9 "vidioc_querycap" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vidioc_querycap \- return capabilities of device
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" vidioc_querycap
.BI "(struct file *file "  ","
.BI "void *priv "  ","
.BI "struct v4l2_capability *cap "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "file" 12
descriptor of device
.IP "priv" 12
unused
.IP "cap" 12
contains return values
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
the capabilities of the device are returned

return value: 0, no error.
